☐ Knowledge captured

---

# Failure Conditions

Reject the experiment if:

Multiple strategic variables change.

No hypothesis exists.

No measurable KPI exists.

No stopping rule exists.

No learning objective exists.

No decision criteria exists.

No knowledge capture exists.

Continue redesigning until every condition is satisfied.

---

# Success Criteria

A successful testing system allows Creative Strategist AI to answer:

What are we validating?

What are we measuring?

How much are we risking?

What will we learn?

When do we stop?

When do we scale?

When do we kill the test?

How does this improve future decisions?

Only then can a test be executed.
